---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Owen Cross"
	description="Senior Software Engineer specialising in .NET, TypeScript and Azure"
	pubDate={new Date('2026-07-01')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		I am Owen Cross, a Senior Software Engineer specialising in .NET, TypeScript and Azure.
	</p>

	<p>
		Most of my work sits around building reliable software, working across modern backend and cloud
		stacks, and keeping things practical instead of overcomplicated.
	</p>

	<p>
		This site is a place for my writing, projects, and anything else worth sharing as I go.
	</p>

	<p>
		You can also find me on GitHub, LinkedIn and X if you want to see what I am up to outside the blog.
	</p>
</Layout>
